<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CineMatrix - Where AI Meets Cinema</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #3b82f6;
            --dark-bg: #1a1a1a;
            --card-bg: #2a2a2a;
            --text-light: #ffffff;
            --text-muted: #9ca3af;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text-light);
            background: var(--dark-bg);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            padding: 80px 0;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)),
                        url('/api/placeholder/1920/1080');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* Features Section */
        .features {
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* Main Sections */
        .main-sections {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .section-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .section-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        .feature-list li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .feature-list li::before {
            content: "→";
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            margin-top: 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .footer a {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1><span style="color: var(--primary-color)">CineMatrix</span></h1>
            <p>Discover films through the lens of artificial intelligence, where every frame tells a deeper story</p>
            </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
                    <h3>Pattern Recognition</h3>
                    <p>Uncover hidden connections and recurring motifs across thousands of films with our advanced pattern detection algorithms.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
                    <h3>Trend Analysis</h3>
                    <p>Track evolving cinematic trends and storytelling patterns across decades of filmmaking.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🎭</div>
                    <h3>Character Insights</h3>
                    <p>Explore detailed character arcs and relationship dynamics through computational narrative analysis.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Sections -->
    <section class="main-sections">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-card">
                <h3>Digital Analysis Lab</h3>
                <p>Step into our virtual laboratory where artificial intelligence dissects the DNA of cinema, revealing the building blocks of great storytelling.</p>
                <ul class="feature-list">
                    <li>Scene-by-scene emotional mapping</li>
                    <li>Visual composition analysis</li>
                    <li>Narrative structure breakdown</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="section-card">
                <h3>Performance Metrics</h3>
                <p>Explore the science behind on-screen chemistry and character portrayal through our advanced performance analysis tools.</p>
                <ul class="feature-list">
                    <li>Actor chemistry calculations</li>
                    <li>Performance consistency tracking</li>
                    <li>Character development mapping</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <p>"See beyond the screen. Understand the science of storytelling."</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>